{"tid":1822734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[下架韓國瑜] 投票率前十高票站，高雄市佔其中七個","createTime":"2020-01-13T06:43:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T11:47:51.000Z","uid":52658,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"5ad8a24501f0a56892913be587782383767c1be0","tid":1822734,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:43:47.000Z","msg":"記者王榮祥／高雄報導<br />\n<br />\n臉書粉專「高雄點」今彙整全國投票率前10高的鄉鎮市區，發<br />\n現全部都在南台灣，其中高雄就佔了7區；小編驚嘆，高雄人真的很憤怒耶。<br />\n<br />\n前10高投票區依序為高雄橋頭區80.55%、屏東麟洛鄉80.15%、高雄彌陀區79.24%<br />\n<br />\n、屏東霧台鄉79.15%、高雄岡山區79.14%、高雄梓官區78.56%、高雄鳥松區78.46%、高雄<br />\n三民區78.31%、高雄鳳山區78.25%、台南歸仁78.21%。<br />\n<br />\n高雄點指出，高雄不但佔了前10高投票區的7席，全高雄投票率77.4%也是六都第一。<br />\n<br />\n網友留言「把高雄當塑膠喔！」、「這麼憤怒、一定要怒吃雞排」、「希望這樣的投票率<br />\n也能反映在接下來的罷免上」、「這就是高雄人的憤怒，還會進化第二階段！」、<span style=\"color: red;\">「高雄<br />\n鄉民表示五月份一定給你高票！」</span>、「我橋頭我驕傲」。"},{"pid":"d7fad0d9f9f559aa3a07527676fe503815411454","tid":1822734,"uid":52658,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:47:43.000Z","msg":"五月份一定給你高票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83f03f175905297df59817d2cd4da0bb7d2bd759","tid":1822734,"uid":52658,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:52:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ComBYkt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FComBYkt.png&h=b78c81de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n笑撚死"},{"pid":"1594d5a12408154a1540bc599429a781a6acd437","tid":1822734,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T07:04:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c5263651e054a4853c21413f59acdae2bbc5394","tid":1822734,"uid":256783,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T07:09:02.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">高雄人 知柒而能改 ? </span></strong>"},{"pid":"aeb5f5c88cabec42ddd9d2d3b11e0e25b4ff5e82","tid":1822734,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6c5263651e